==Economy== The economy is based around food and construction materials industries.<ref name="Great"/> Natural gas is also extracted in the area.
==Sights== *Close to Baýramaly are the ruins of ancient [[Merv]]. *{{convert|28|km|mi}} to the north is the mausoleum of Hudaýnazar Öwlüýä (early 12th century).<ref name="Great"/>
